  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Study of the kinetics of uremic toxins in the ICU patients with acute renal failure, in order
      to optimize the dialysis dose: patients after cardiac surgery.The sampling of blood and
      dialysate will be done during dialyses with different durations (4, 6 and 8h)
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
